Culture Medium: DMEM:F12 + 0.00625 mg/ml insulin; 0.00625 mg/ml transferrin; 6.25 ng/ml selenium; 1.25 mg/ml bovine serum albumin; 0.00535 mg/ml linoleic acid; adjust to a final concentration of 2.5% Nu-Serum I. The additives (insulin, transferrin, selenium, BSA and linoleic acid) are available in the form of ITS+ Premix from Corning (Catalog No. 354352). Nu-Serum is also available from Corning (Catalog No. 355100).
